Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.11,0:00:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.22,0:00:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.59,0:00:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这还真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.86,0:00:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得如何？八房
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.70,0:00:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错 我觉得很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.61,0:00:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来找龙帮忙是找对了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.79,0:00:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.41,0:00:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:00:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见习宫廷药剂师 志愿者审查期
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.21,0:01:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不总是很在意 整个人坐立不安的嘛 千
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚迈出第一步的这条道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟会是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何种形状
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何种色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何种气味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天还不曾了解的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.59,0:01:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若今天能有所了解的话
